- Lint with `eslint` (Airbnb-TypeScript + import/order).
- Format with `prettier`; enforce via Husky & `lint-staged` on pre-commit.
- Run unit tests and type-check in pre-push hook.
- Provide Dockerfile per service; dev containers use VS Code dev-containers images.
